Description: Design and analysis of flexible platform trials with non-concurrent controls. Functions for data generation, analysis, visualization and running simulation studies are provided. 
    The implemented analysis methods are described in: 
    Bofill Roig et al. (2022) <https://doi.org/10.1186/s12874-022-01683-w>, 
    Saville et al. (2022) <https://doi.org/10.1177/17407745221112013> and 
    Schmidli et al. (2014) <https://doi.org/10.1111/biom.12242>.
URL: https://pavlakrotka.github.io/NCC/, https://github.com/pavlakrotka/NCC
